ActNavigable Waters Protection Act
SubjectProclamation Exempting the Mink Arm portion of South McMahon Lake from the Operation of Section 22 of the Act
PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION be issued declaring that the WATERS OF THE MINK ARM PORTION OF SOUTH MCMAHON LAKE, located in Saskatchewan, be exempt from the operation of section 22 of the Navigable Waters Protection Act with respect to the depositing of waste mining materials by AREVA Resources Canada Inc.
